Name: FileName
Description: Name of the file being merged.  May be the name of an active dataframe.

Name: MergeType
Description: Describes the type of merge performed.
Enumeration: Sequential OneToOne ManyToOne OneToMany Cartesian Unmatched SASmatchMerge

Name: MergeFlagVariable
Description: Name of a new variable indicating whether the row came from this file or a different input file.

Name: Overlap
Description: Outcome when the same variables exist in more than one file. "Master" is the default value.  "Ignore" means values in this file are never used.  "FillNew is used on rows not found in the ""Master"" data frame.  ""UpdateMissing"" replaces missing values in the ""Master"" datafram. "Replace" changes all values in the ""Master"" dataframe."

Name: NewRow
Description: When TRUE,  generate new row when not matched to other files
